There is also a piece of parchment which reads as follows:<br>
<br>
<!--EZCODE FONT START--><span style="font-size:x-small;">&quot;Each person may draw cards from this deck. You must announce how many cards you wish to draw before you begin, you must draw exactly that amount of cards, each within one hour of each other. After you draw your allotted cards from the deck, you may never draw from it again.<br>
